 <H1>Learning and Costs</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Minimize cost of making classifications
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Learner has free access to all attributes of training data
<LI>Learner has knowledge of cost of testing each attribute
<LI>Reduce cost of accurately classifying test example
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Minimize cost of errors made by classifier
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>Not all errors are equally important
<LI>Costs depend on the predicted class and the actual class</UL></UL></P>
